      "content": "<div class=\"souhait-container\">\n  <h1 class=\"souhait-title\">Que souhaitez-vous faire ?</h1>\n  <p class=\"souhait-subtitle\">Veuillez choisir une option ci-dessous pour continuer</p>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n  .souhait-container {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\n    padding: 0 15px;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n  }\n  \n  .souhait-title {\n    color: #006A4F;\n    margin: 0;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    font-size: 52px;\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n  }\n  \n  .souhait-subtitle {\n    color: #6B7280;\n    margin: 16px 0 0 0;\n    font-size: 18px;\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n  }\n  \n  @media (max-width: 992px) {\n    .souhait-title {\n      font-size: 40px;\n    }\n    \n    .souhait-subtitle {\n      font-size: 16px;\n    }\n  }\n  \n  @media (max-width: 576px) {\n    .souhait-container {\n      margin-bottom: 24px;\n    }\n    \n    .souhait-title {\n      font-size: 28px;\n    }\n    \n    .souhait-subtitle {\n      font-size: 14px;\n      padding: 0 10px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>",
